Author: itsmebutprivate
Text: I did that Saturday and ate an entire pizza. (Italian restaurant kind, none of that franchised stuff). I was on the verge of tears from pain. Like I could physically feel my stomach stretching.   But after that I restricted for a couple of days and everything’s back to normal ¯\_(ツ)_/¯   “Everybody makes mistakes”-Hannah

Author: LowCalPal
Text: Just like one day restricting won’t make you skinny, one day of bingeing won’t make you fat.  Back on the wagon tomorrow <3
